description: Ten new chicks are born at Curraghs Wildlife Park as part of an international breeding programme.
title: 'Phenomenal year' for Humboldt penguins at Isle of Man wildlife park
title_page: 'Phenomenal year' for Humboldt penguins at Isle of Man wildlife park - BBC News
maintext: Park manager Kathleen Graham said the new arrivals were a "major success story" for the park's breeding programme and for her team, "who have worked so hard throughout lockdown".
